MindCare is a mobile mental health counseling application designed for university students who need confidential, compassionate and accessible emotional support. The app provides structured access to professional counseling services, self-help resources, mood tracking tools and urgent crisis support guidance in one calm and easy-to-use platform.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar\loch

